OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan, 78, died 'after       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fburglar tied him to chair' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An elderly man died after being tied to
OL,6, a chair by a burglar who returned more 
OL,7, than a week later to free his victim's 
OL,8, body, a jury has heard.                
OL,10,FDavid Varlow, 78, was found dead when  
OL,11,Fpolice forced entry to his home in     
OL,12,FManor Lane, Halesowen, in November.    
OL,14,FAdris Mohammed, 44, went back to the   
OL,15,Fproperty knowing Mr Varlow would be    
OL,16,Fdead and to steal more items,          
OL,17,FBirmingham Crown Court was told.       
OL,19,FMr Mohammed denies charges of murder,  
OL,20,Fmanslaughter, fraud and burglary.      
